n=eval(input("Enter the number:"))
sp=0
sn=0
cp=0
cn=0
while(n!=-1):
    if(n>0):
         cp+=1
        sp+=n
    else:
        cn+=1
        sn+=n
    n=eval(input("Enter the number:"))
if(cn>0):
    print("the average of negative",sn/cn)
else:
    print("no negative numbers are entered")
if(cp>0):
    print("the average of postive",sp/cp)
else:
    print("no postive numbers are entered")

OUTPUT:
Enter the number:1
Enter the number:6
Enter the number:-2
Enter the number:-4
Enter the number:-5
Enter the number:6
Enter the number:9
Enter the number:-1
the average of negative -3.6666666666666665
the average of postive 5.5
